{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-03T19:01:13Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":81,"issue_id":"workspace-svs","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"workspace-svs\",\"title\":\"[security] Audit event FK ordering in provisioning D1 batch\",\"description\":\"File: specs/012-clawtask-vertical-slice/plan.md (Security Considerations)\\nSeverity: Critical\\n\\nProblem:\\nAudit events in the D1 batch must be inserted last — foreign keys on workspace_id, actor_id, etc. must exist before audit events reference them, or the batch will fail with FK constraint errors.\\n\\nFix:\\nOrder D1 batch statements: 1) workspace, 2) actor, 3) areas+contexts, 4) audit events. Verify FK ordering in WorkspaceProvisioningService.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:14:57Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:14:57Z\"}"}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-03T19:12:06Z","event_type":"closed","id":82,"issue_id":"workspace-svs","new_value":"Closed","old_value":""}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-03T19:12:53Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":83,"issue_id":"workspace-35c","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"workspace-35c\",\"title\":\"[security] Empty actor ID in requireWorkspace must 503, not fall through\",\"description\":\"File: specs/012-clawtask-vertical-slice/plan.md (Security Considerations)\\nSeverity: Critical\\n\\nProblem:\\nrequireWorkspace middleware must return 503 when actor ID is empty — falling through with empty string produces silent data corruption (audit events with empty actor_id, actions owned by nobody).\\n\\nFix:\\nAdd explicit check: if (!actorId) return c.json({ error: 'Workspace not provisioned' }, 503);\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:14:54Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:14:54Z\"}"}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-03T19:16:27Z","event_type":"closed","id":84,"issue_id":"workspace-35c","new_value":"Implemented requireWorkspace middleware with explicit actor null check returning 503. Created WorkspaceRepository and ActorRepository interfaces, updated AppEnv.Variables with workspaceId and actorId, and added 9 tests covering all security paths.","old_value":""}
{"actor":"eykd","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-03T19:17:33Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":85,"issue_id":"workspace-gib","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"workspace-gib\",\"title\":\"[security] TOCTOU race on clarification — missing optimistic lock\",\"description\":\"File: specs/012-clawtask-vertical-slice/plan.md (Security Considerations)\\nSeverity: Critical\\n\\nProblem:\\nClarification action has TOCTOU race condition — needs optimistic lock via WHERE status = 'inbox' in the UPDATE statement to prevent double-clarification of the same inbox item.\\n\\nFix:\\nImplement atomic conditional UPDATE: UPDATE inbox_item SET status='clarified' WHERE id=? AND status='inbox'; check rows affected = 1 before proceeding.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"david@worldsenoughstudios.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:14:51Z\",\"created_by\":\"eykd\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T17:14:51Z\"}"}
